Description:
Farming - Lifestyle - Dairy - Irrigation
100 acres or 40.50 Ha situated between Cobram and Yarroweyah on Montgomery Road.
DAIRY FARM, CROPPING/GRAZING/IRRIGATION PROPERTY
● Three bedroom renovated timber family home with open plan living
and updated kitchen.
● The farm is 80% lasered with a good mix of permanent pasture and
annuals all growing in Moira sandy loam soils. The farm has
recently been re-fenced with good laneways.
● 18 aside dairy complete with modern plant, in-bale feed system,
4000 litre vat, 200 cow yard with good drafting facilities and
very good calf rearing facilities.
● Stock and domestic deep lead bore supplying troughs, dairy
and home. GMW delivery share in place.
● Until recently this property was in full production. It would
make a great investment property and agistment block.
● Modern two bedroom cottage that is less than five years old and
was recently rented at approx $320 per week
● Being sold in conjunction with Sallan Realty of Cobram
Please call Sharon Cain 0358 712029

Description:
A UNIQUE RURAL LIFESTYLE OPPORTUNITY
• Land Area: 26.4 acres - 10.7 hectares on 1 title
• Recently renovated four bedroom home set in an old established garden
• Ample shedding including a 40x20ft lockup shed and a 36x18ft open front shed
• Fertile red sandy loam soils serviced by fixed spray irrigation

• Inspections strictly by appointment with the Exclusive selling agents

Description:
VENDORS MOVING NORTH KEEN TO SELL!
Peaceful lifestyle Living
With 26 squares of living your family need not wait any longer – with space for all with rural lifestyle. Situated on 3.3 acres of beautiful grounds with established garden and trees.
Spacious craftsman built 5 bedroom home, master with large ensuite and walk in robe. 9 ft ceilings throughout, large kitchen, walk in pantry, dishwasher, gas stove cook top and electric oven. The kitchen is complemented with a cathedral ceiling and a good size family/living area which leads into the formal lounge/dining area. Three bathrooms, main with corner spa, second bedroom with disability bathroom and walk in robe.
Other features include evaporative cooling, floor heating, new decked undercover entertaining area, 10kw (40 panels) solar system. This home has recently had an update, with new kitchen, carpets, window furbishings, bathrooms, laundry, toilets and freshly painted throughout.
Outside you will be impressed with what this property has to offer. A large 24 metre x 12 metre shed which also holds a 7.2 metre x 4.8 metre spray booth, all comes with power and concrete flooring this will be any handyman’s delight. There are 6 megs of commercial bore water and 2 megs of stock and domestic. A well maintained vege garden and small orchard of cherry trees. The property is irrigated by in ground sprinkler system.
GREAT FOR THE HOME BASED SMALL BUSINESS!
Internal area
26m²

Description:
Ultimate Family Living Lifestyle - Reduced to $375,000
This immaculate 5 bedroom property is perfect for the large family who needs space and loves to entertain! You enter through the solid feature front door, to be greeted by an open plan living/kitchen/dining. The living is spacious in size, enjoys a projector and screen for your entertainment and flows to the dining and galley style kitchen which comprises walk in pantry, dishwasher and electric appliances. All bedrooms are double or bigger and offer built in robes with the master bedroom spoilt with a walk in robe. There are two family bathrooms, one with corner spa with shower over, vanity and toilet whilst the other has large vanity, shower and toilet. Climate throughout is controlled by gas ducted heating, ceiling fans and evaporative air conditioning. Externally you will be amazed at whats on offer. A huge entertainment area, makes this home ideal to relax and entertain with family and friends, with its own open fireplace to add to the charm. Imagine sitting back enjoying a glass of wine, whilst watching the kids enjoy a swim in the in-ground swimming pool. Add to this an enormous 20m x 11.5m industrial shed with three phase power and highway frontage, perfect for a business or hobby. This wonderful home certainly ticks all the boxes! Call for an inspection now!

Irreplacable at the money!!

Description:
"Carwelkin" Lagoon Frontage Koonoomoo
A magnificent treed setting. 13.74 Ha (33 Acres) set up with irrigation. The residence features an open living plan & well appointed kitchen. 3 bedrooms with full ensuite & parents retreat in main bedroom, office or 4th BR, ducted evap air condit, R/C air condit, infloor heating & Coonara wood heater. Huge U/C entertaining area with spa bath, 5KW solar power system, self contained cabin (rents out for extra income), 3 car carport & fernery. 2 stables, numerous sheds & 7 holding plus day paddocks. Filtered bore, rainwater tanks & recycle dam. 30 ML water available by negotiation.
A fantastic rural lifestyle.
